rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0001
rows.name:
How did you find it, visiting your
hometown after so long?

rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0002
rows.name:
I was surprised how much the kids had
grown, but apart from that, it was all
just how I remembered. Which is nice.

rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0003
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm all rested up and
raring to go! I'm ready to lead
the way to the port.

rows.label: fev05_150_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, it's not like it's very far.
It's just on the next island over.
